(ns o2w.api.core
  (:refer-clojure :exclude [get atom])
  (:require [o2w.api.impl :as impl]
            [o2w.api.atom]
            [ajax.url :as url]
            [o2w.api.data :as data]))

(def req impl/req)
(def call impl/req)
(def source data/source)
(defn get [endpoint args] (req endpoint args))
(defn post [endpoint args] (req endpoint (merge {:method :post} args)))
(defn delete [endpoint args] (req endpoint (merge {:method :delete} args)))
(defn put [endpoint args] (req endpoint (merge {:method :put} args)))
(defn patch [endpoint args] (req endpoint (merge {:method :patch} args)))

(def get-auth-token impl/get-token)
(def set-auth-token! impl/set-token)
(def clear-auth-token! impl/clear-token)

(defn configure [new-config]
  (swap! impl/config merge new-config))

;; (defn << [path & [args]] (rf/subscribe [:api/subscribe path args]))
;; (defn >> [path value] (rf/dispatch [:api/assoc-in path value]))
;; (defn <<! [path & [args]] (rf/dispatch [:api/fetch path args]))
(def params-to-str (partial url/params-to-str :java))

(defn params-clean [params]
  (into {} (filter second params)))

(def atom o2w.api.atom/remote-atom)
(def refresh! o2w.api.atom/refresh!)
(def clean! o2w.api.atom/clean!)
